// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-3080 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 58e3f389-006d-5a28-975c-2296c996f5de

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:1*" or process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:7*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*")
